short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Step into a world of mystery and suspense with the Dark Huntress in a Haunted Landscape Live Wallpaper.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension features a fierce and enigmatic huntress navigating a chilling, haunted landscape. Watch as the eerie atmosphere unfolds with dynamic effects, capturing the dark beauty of the huntress as she explores the ghostly surroundings, bringing a touch of intrigue and adventure to your browser.

Features:
🏹 Mysterious live wallpaper of a Dark Huntress in a haunted landscape.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display to stay organized.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for easy navigation to your favorite websites.
Let the haunting beauty of this dark huntress transform your browsing experience every time you open a new tab.
